OL,3,CMan charged with murder of mum shot
OL,4,Cdead in Sheffield
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the murder
OL,7,Fof a mother-of-one who was shot dead
OL,8,Foutside a bar in Sheffield.
OL,10,FShanice Brookes, 30, died after an
OL,11,Fincident at One Four One, on West
OL,12,FStreet, in the early hours of Bank
OL,13,FHoliday Monday, 25 May.
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire Police said she was an
OL,16,Finnocent bystander who was caught in
OL,17,Fthe cross-fire following an
OL,18,Faltercation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
