OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1780387618
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of mum shot
OL,4,Cdead in Sheffield
OL,6,FJemele Rhone, 30, of Outram Road,
OL,7,FSheffield, has now been charged with
OL,8,Fmurder, possession of a firearm and
OL,9,Fpossession of criminal property.
OL,11,FDeiryen Dyce, 32, of Ellesmere Road
OL,12,FNorth, Sheffield, has been charged
OL,13,Fwith assisting an offender.
OL,15,FShe is also charged with possession of
OL,16,Fammunition, drugs offences and
OL,17,Fpossession of criminal property.
OL,19,FBoth are due to appear at Sheffield
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court on Friday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
