FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1780387618
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of mum shot
OL,4,Cdead in Sheffield
OL,6,FA 30-year-old man arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder has been released
OL,8,Fwithout charge.
OL,10,FDet Ch Insp Andy Knowles said:
OL,11,F"Shanice's family, including her young
OL,12,Fson, now face the harrowing reality
OL,13,Fthat they will never get to see her
OL,14,Fagain.
OL,16,F"They are having to grieve the
OL,17,Funimaginable loss of their beloved
OL,18,Fdaughter, friend and mother in the
OL,19,Fmost tragic of circumstances. Our
OL,20,Fthoughts remain with them.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
