OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1780387618
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of mum shot
OL,4,Cdead in Sheffield
OL,6,F"From the outset of this investigation
OL,7,Four priority has been clear - to
OL,8,Fprovide answers for Shanice's loved
OL,9,Fones - and today's development is a
OL,10,Fsignificant step in our commitment to
OL,11,Fdo so."
OL,13,FHe added: "Monday's incident has shown
OL,14,Fhow gun crime destroys families and
OL,15,Fbrings devastation to our communities.
OL,16,FWe need your help to ensure other
OL,17,Ffamilies never have to experience the
OL,18,Funthinkable pain and loss Shanice's
OL,19,Floved ones are currently having to
OL,20,Fcome to terms with."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
